com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.directions.helperclasses

Class Segment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.directions.helperclasses.Segment

  • public class Segment
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstraction of segment object, shows the total distance and duration of it, it's steps, start and end waypoints. There might be ascent, descent, average speed, detour factor and percentage values, but they can be null.
    Author:
    Marcos Henrique
